{"tid":1879713,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"潮文共享：歐美正妹(3)","createTime":"2020-02-14T10:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T05:34:17.000Z","uid":143367,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c45b1f37e5a7c0118b57507d593aa36592a0c3e4","tid":1879713,"uid":143367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:56:39.000Z","msg":"上一個POST<br />\n歐美正妹<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1873713\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1873713</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我叫周顯成，大家可以叫我做雞蟲成或者笠水成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年係香海正覺蓮社佛教馬錦燦紀念英文中學讀緊4A班，A班精英班黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jpUTP0g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjpUTP0g.png&h=ed89f972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個我ig，歡迎女女follow我，我有做運動今年中四實屌撚到你地有性病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說我之前係成人台開左個post<br />\n歐美正妹<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1873713\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1873713</a><br />\n<br />\n身為雞蟲，有好野緊係想同連登巴絲打一齊些牙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kaPwBGc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkaPwBGc.png&h=ad1908ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係有班撚樣話我Cap圖cap埋自己icon好柒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BT98DVC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBT98DVC.png&h=6be52e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張我icon明明就影得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一心諗住上黎分享，居然走上黎踩我場，話我柒話我讀中四點點點&hellip;&hellip;屌你老母嬲撚到我紅到面晒，望住moon手都震埋，呀呀呀呀呀啊啊啊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，我要扮到完全唔在乎，因為我讀中四又有做運動，分分鐘一拳打撚死呢班青頭死毒撚，同我玩?你班友真係未夠班，仲要貼我上黎?<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">So what</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明在座各位仲柒過我，幾時輪到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都知連登多毒撚，點知佢地係都要沖出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住有一個叫做一齊攬炒既青頭死毒撚Jer9住我，一直話9我弱智<br />\n我真係有少少弱智，但唔係比你咁樣周街唱囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀!!!!!好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>你估屌人唔駛付出代價？<br />\n唔敢出聲叫on9仔<br />\n凈係回擊你已經算好<br />\n我認我係咸濕<br />\n有咩問題 你都一樣姐<br />\n我入唔入嚟又關你咩事啊<br />\n攬炒契弟<br />\n唔好以為自己大過我就好撚巴閉<br />\n你都係頭入嚟個批人<br />\n我無話想得罪邊個<br />\n不過你條仆街進嚟撩尻我 都幾好嘢<br />\n幾大啊你 2字頭3字頭定話4字頭？<br />\n都唔細啦 咁唔成熟<br />\n唔好以為上嚟發洩我就唔敢還擊<br />\n你老母上嚟callin都唔夠膽啦<br />\n我中唔中四又關你撚事？<br />\n中四唔撚俾咸濕？<br />\n駛唔駛戒埋淫慾啊<br />\n你自己呢個年紀同我咪差唔多<br />\n雙重標準<br />\n話我入嚟成人台係弱智<br />\n咁你咪仲撚弱智<br />\n你自己都睇緊啦<br />\n講撚咗幾多次<br />\n你有你道理你拎出嚟講<br />\n無事撩尻我 咁樣叫柒<br />\n我做咩柒事 柒得過你咁撚幼稚咩<br />\n我而家屌撚醒你班連登仔<br />\n咪撚咁幼稚 你IG又擺咩icon啊<br />\n有幾成熟？<br />\n係成熟你都唔會理我啦 你老母<br />\n我未撚出社會個邏輯都正路過你啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒契弟</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我讀中四，好撚過你班連登青頭毒撚多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢條友講嘢都無內容，讀多d書啦你老母，我仲要有做運動一拳打撚死你條青頭毒撚呀<br />\n你咁有道理咪拎你d point出嚟講囉<br />\n又無又要死挺 同你講都無用啦，同你講咁多都晒口水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入正題，依家佢地連我steam都起埋出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nif7T1i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnif7T1i.png&h=662c689d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGSuouB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGSuouB.jpg&h=9b97b6e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連我屋企人我同學都知我有Call g，成身性病又有愛滋仲有我細佬唔能掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求求大家高抬貴手 唔好再Jer我了<br />\n同埋求求Admin幫我del post thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ndel post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/faALJS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/faALJS</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"538c1f1f2f81f5c271e656c0037f35ca0328d672","tid":1879713,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"咁撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72aa0c32f32b56592a9dd1a9aab7d7c8d255abf7","tid":1879713,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:58:19.000Z","msg":"2推完拿？"},{"pid":"bda3ebb685d23393cd42b84e95de9608eeceed1b","tid":1879713,"uid":143367,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"成哥上成人台屌柒連登仔這麼勇,你班主任知道嗎"},{"pid":"6a4f201652658937f849703cd3d0f88b34ce6670","tid":1879713,"uid":300241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:00:13.000Z","msg":"果然得罪邊個都可以，得罪連登仔就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0759bcb6183d0e3312484a39b74abc4c1009db30","tid":1879713,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"最後嗰張唔夠喉呀，得個膊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b161da331f83c47c1a079a6fb87f471c51bfb766","tid":1879713,"uid":135693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"喂 你地好大壓力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f3a19ce74b1ac3d14e1d9be3339c81704a5ea7","tid":1879713,"uid":229